title: SIC! SIC! SIC!
html:
SIC! SIC! SIC!

“We will oil your sewing machine and adjust the tension in your home for $1.00.” [Heard on Radio KBOR in Brownsville, Texas on June 5, 1985. Submitted by Max R. Tyner, McAllen, Texas.]
